# Blog Cards Behavior

- Blog list and related-post cards should stay visually aligned.
- Show title and description by default for normal posts.
- Show compact hashtag label on hover when tag is available.
- For `#книги` cards:
  - keep title visible,
  - hide description,
  - render book cover without decorative frame/background,
  - use `object-fit: contain` (no crop).
- Tag color semantics must stay consistent:
  - `#книги` blue,
  - `#лидерство` warm orange,
  - `#ценности` green.
- Card border color should match tag color when a tag is present.
